Package flex2.tools.oem.internal

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ApplicationCompilerConfiguration
    A configuration that extends ToolsConfiguration by adding options for -file-specs, -include-resource-bundles, -load-config, and -projector.
    BuilderLogger
    A Logger implementation, which adds messages to a passed in List and delegates to a passed in Logger if not null.
    LibraryCompilerConfiguration
    A configuration that extends CompcConfiguration by adding options for -loadConfig and -compute-digest.
    LinkerConfiguration
    A configuration that extends ToolsConfiguration by adding link specific options.
    OEMConfiguration
    A ToolsConfiguration wrapper, which provides strongly typed configuration getters and setters, which internally storing them loosely typed for later processing.
    OEMConsole
    An OEM API logger implementation that outputs using System.err and System.out.
    OEMLogAdapter
    Extends AbstractLogger to support logging to an OEM API logger.
    OEMReport
    A Report implementation.
    OEMUtil
    A collection of utility methods used by classes in flex2.tools.oem.
